**[[航空自衛隊|航空自衛隊]]（230架）：1962年10月到1986年間服役於日本空中自衛隊，使用210架F-104J和20架F-104DJ，日本稱為'''榮光'''，服役期間損失了總共3架飛機。包括一次空中碰撞事故，F-104J/DJ服役於7個中隊：201,202,203,204,205,206,207。在自衛隊服役期間，F-104J為攔截蘇聯軍機的主力戰機。31架F-104J和5架F-104DJ退役後出售給中華民國<ref>[http://www.taiwanairpower.org/history/f104ret.html ROCAF F-104 Retirement] {{Wayback|url=http://www.taiwanairpower.org/history/f104ret.html |date=20190226114548 }} Retrieved September 30, 2017</ref><ref>[http://www.i-f-s.nl/preserved-f-104s/preserved-in-taiwan/ Preserved in Taiwan] {{Wayback|url=http://www.i-f-s.nl/preserved-f-104s/preserved-in-taiwan/ |date=20190330170157 }} ''International F-104 Society'' Retrieved September 30, 2017</ref><ref>[http://www.916-starfighter.de/F-104_RoCAF_serials.htm 916 Starfighter] {{Wayback|url=http://www.916-starfighter.de/F-104_RoCAF_serials.htm |date=20190330170240 }} Retrieved September 30, 2017</ref><ref>[http://www.ejection-history.org.uk/Country-By-Country/Taiwan.htm Ejection History - Taiwan] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ejection-history.org.uk/Country-By-Country/Taiwan.htm |date=20090107050559 }} Retrieved September 30, 2017</ref>
